    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable driver with a bit of character. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some typical wear and tear consistent with its age, such as minor oil seepage and a slightly aged suspension. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading paint on the hood, while the interior shows signs of use with some wear on the upholstery. It is a dependable car that is ready for the road, but it will eventually benefit from some cosmetic and minor mechanical attention to bring it back to its best.",
